{"tid":198912,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[明報新聞] 魯爾：C朗年紀漸大失速度","createTime":"2017-04-12T21:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T02:02:05.000Z","uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30c0ed306439ed856591da36f664333fd6281a9f","tid":198912,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DS082Wi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDS082Wi.jpg&h=8afacefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】皇家馬德里名宿前鋒魯爾表示，年紀漸大已令32歲的基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗拿度）開始走下坡，但仍信對方的水準勝隊友。<br />\n<br />\n魯爾說：「C朗拿度失去速度，隨着年紀漸大，這是正常的，但他仍有質素，水平仍高於皇馬隊友。」C朗拿度今季上陣33次入26球，相比於過去6季場均入逾1球明顯遜色，當中踢足歐聯8戰只入2球更惹人詬病，魯爾續說：「他或者正嘗試減少單打獨鬥。不過，這也是他不習慣之處。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a713afe22838524af0dc1c6eebb37918568f131","tid":198912,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:22:00.000Z","msg":"水平仍高於皇馬隊友。"},{"pid":"be3cd905d65e0dc3d0fdaf582b43d5546f694d0b","tid":198912,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:23:43.000Z","msg":"有幾多前鋒32歲仲係頂班?"},{"pid":"a87ed1d5666955dedffc291599a5406e4b901655","tid":198912,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:25:06.000Z","msg":"33場入26球都唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d83fb250b543ff2643748502f7501cf62af3950","tid":198912,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:27:51.000Z","msg":"廢魯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"3cdbd22b02d9b4335e1ef54397c5a21aebbdce94","tid":198912,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾多前鋒32歲仲係頂班?</blockquote><br />\n<br /